trans-unit.source: An activity that executes all child activities simultaneously and asynchronously.
trans-unit.target: En aktivitet som utför alla underordnade aktiviteter samtidigt och asynkront.

trans-unit.source: A Parallel activity operates by simultaneously scheduling each <xref:System.Activities.Activity> in its <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A> collection at the start.
trans-unit.target: En parallell aktivitet fungerar genom att schemalägga samtidigt varje <xref:System.Activities.Activity>i dess <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A>samling i början.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Activity>

trans-unit.source: It completes when all of its <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A> complete or when its <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.CompletionCondition%2A> property evaluates to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Den är klar när alla dess <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A>slutförts eller när dess <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.CompletionCondition%2A>egenskapen utvärderas till `true`.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.CompletionCondition%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A>

trans-unit.source: While all the <xref:System.Activities.Activity> objects run asynchronously, they do not execute on separate threads, so each successive activity only executes when the previously scheduled activity completes or goes idle.
trans-unit.target: När alla de <xref:System.Activities.Activity>objekt körs asynkront, de inte köras på olika trådar, så att varje efterföljande aktivitet körs endast när tidigare schemalagd aktivitet har slutförts eller försätts inaktiv.</xref:System.Activities.Activity>

trans-unit.source: If none of the child activities of this activity go idle, this activity execute in the same way that a <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Sequence> activity does.
trans-unit.target: Om ingen av de underordnade aktiviteterna i den här aktiviteten går inaktiv köra aktiviteten på samma sätt som en <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Sequence>aktivitet gör.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.Sequence>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.Parallel"></xref> activity.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.Parallel"> </xref> aktivitet.

trans-unit.source: If this property evaluates to `true`, then the other scheduled elements in the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A> collection are canceled.
trans-unit.target: Om den här egenskapen evalueras till `true`, sedan de andra schemalagda element i den <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A>samling har avbrutits.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A>

trans-unit.source: If this property is not set, all <xref:System.Activities.Activity> objects in the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A> collection execute until completion.
trans-unit.target: Om den här egenskapen inte anges visas alla <xref:System.Activities.Activity>objekt i den <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A>samling köras tills den har slutförts.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.Parallel.Branches%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Activity>
